{"tid":218590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家食番石榴食唔食中間","createTime":"2017-04-26T15:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T02:58:11.000Z","uid":112020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c61a96727b10455e19a935632b191166afd889","tid":218590,"uid":112020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"5fe73edb31bef533845502d8021ea3c5cbc47c78","tid":218590,"uid":20934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"140c46aa5c5345e8906ab84fa5f2ad895f73874e","tid":218590,"uid":112020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔食中間不如唔好食</blockquote><br />\n我由細到大都食 岩岩rmmate食番石榴整走左中間 話食左會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5efc885e1a5939aa6b842aafc7451525f569a1","tid":218590,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔食中間不如唔好食</blockquote><br />\n我由細到大都食 岩岩rmmate食番石榴整走左中間 話食左會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食中間幫手清腸道黐住嘅大便<br />\n即係同食高纖維嘅食品作用一樣(其實番石榴就係高纖食品)<br />\n食完要飲多d水先易排出<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20160223/0/26/49/阿媽教落-吃番石榴不去核會便祕嗎-5445990.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20160223%2F0%2F26%2F49%2F%E9%98%BF%E5%AA%BD%E6%95%99%E8%90%BD-%E5%90%83%E7%95%AA%E7%9F%B3%E6%A6%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%8E%BB%E6%A0%B8%E6%9C%83%E4%BE%BF%E7%A5%95%E5%97%8E-5445990.html&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e91722a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20160223/0/26/49/阿媽教落-吃番石榴不去核會便祕嗎-5445990.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e00db9fecbf31e6faba0b22ef7d1a2cd47970a3","tid":218590,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"中間先係最好食<br />\n買完翻黎有咁耐擺咁耐<br />\n擺翻個𡃁兩個禮拜，等到啲香氣由入面滲出黎<br />\n一切開，嘩！啲果肉同個心一樣咁軟林林<br />\n一咬落去介乎果凍同漿糊之間既口感充斥住你嘅口腔<br />\n咀嚼嘅時候要輕輕力，唔咬爛啲核，妹下妹下用條利咁將番石榴肉團推向口入面每個角落<br />\n吞左之後仲要呵啖氣聞𠴱陣清新哪果香果"},{"pid":"6683e88e50be81bf9fa4bf851b9873afc144445e","tid":218590,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中間先係最好食<br />\n買完翻黎有咁耐擺咁耐<br />\n擺翻個𡃁兩個禮拜，等到啲香氣由入面滲出黎<br />\n一切開，嘩！啲果肉同個心一樣咁軟林林<br />\n一咬落去介乎果凍同漿糊之間既口感充斥住你嘅口腔<br />\n咀嚼嘅時候要輕輕力，唔咬爛啲核，妹下妹下用條利咁將番石榴肉團推向口入面每個角落<br />\n吞左之後仲要呵啖氣聞𠴱陣清新哪果香果</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32e6338b6e37c350f43e34f91bd0f54e3cead8c","tid":218590,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題</blockquote><br />\n但係台灣𠴱隻硬過石頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食唔過"}]}